# **Duke Skip**

The&nbsp;**Duke Skip**&nbsp;allows the player to skip the entire prison area of [The Duke's Archives,](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/the-duke-s-archives) including the otherwise required death on the first encounter with&nbsp;[Seath the Scaleless](https://darksouls.wikidot.com/seath-the-scaleless). It was found by **Aihel** in 2011 on PTDE version of the game.

## **External resources**

### Glitchless Method

The skip is executed on the last elevator before the first Seath the Scaleless encounter. After pulling the lever of this elevator you walk, sprint or roll off it before it starts moving downwards, then roll or fall onto the right corner railing of the elevator while it's moving, giving you the opportunity to roll onto the 3rd floor of the Duke's Archives.

- Duke Skip with Bow [https://youtu.be/Zs7m-cXytK0](https://youtu.be/Zs7m-cXytK0) by QueueKyoo on YouTube.
- Duke skip without Bow [https://youtu.be/nrVrBWPllTg ](https://youtu.be/nrVrBWPllTg)by Catalystz on YouTube.
- Duke skip alternative with a Bow [https://youtu.be/lChnXjTAK14](https://youtu.be/lChnXjTAK14) by San on YouTube.

### **Glitched Method**

The glitched method use the [elevator upwarp](/ds1remaster/elevator-upwarp) glitch to get out of bounce.

- Duke skip with [memeroll / FC Quit-Out](/ds1remaster/fall-damages-cancel)  [https://youtu.be/EocCG10TLEs](https://youtu.be/EocCG10TLEs) by San on YouTube.
- Duke skip example in a run [https://youtu.be/BLm2a6vfCLg?t=1684](https://youtu.be/BLm2a6vfCLg?t=1684) by M3dic on YouTube.
